data.description: Enjoy the lake life at Seneca in this lovely ranch style home that is in walking to distance to the lake, where you will have dock rights! This home features 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and a spacious lot consisting of 3 parcels in total. It is move in ready and has newer flooring throughout. It also has a new roof, heat pump, and central air unit. An oversized garage with attached full bath perfect for coming in from a long day on the lake or entertaining from the back deck. There are also 3 sheds on the property equipped with electric for all of your storage needs. Going inside from the back deck you will walk into the eat in kitchen that is right next to the living room which features a beautiful stone fireplace. On one side of the home there are 2 bedrooms with a shared full bath. On the opposite side of the home you will find the owners suite which is also conveniently located next to the laundry room.
